---
description: This project uses Caliber for automatic AI agent context sync
alwaysApply: true
---
This project uses Caliber to keep AI agent configs (CLAUDE.md, Cursor rules, Copilot instructions)
in sync with the codebase automatically. Before each commit, run `/opt/homebrew/bin/caliber refresh` to sync configs.
If `/opt/homebrew/bin/caliber` is not found, read the setup-caliber skill from .cursor/skills/setup-caliber/SKILL.md and follow its instructions to install Caliber.
